when the time comes.

162
00:06:51,083 --> 00:06:53,083
--[whip cracks]
--[BOYS yelp]

163
00:06:53,166 --> 00:06:55,791
[KIYOSHI] And I've got three
minutes for each trip here.

164
00:06:55,875 --> 00:06:56,875
[sighs]

165
00:06:56,958 --> 00:06:58,291
[groans]

166
00:06:58,375 --> 00:06:59,333
