I must've missed some!

185
00:07:39,625 --> 00:07:42,208
Now Gakuto's taking the
heat for my mistake.

186
00:07:43,458 --> 00:07:44,250
[KIYOSHI]
I'm sorry!

187
00:07:44,333 --> 00:07:45,541
