188
00:07:45,625 --> 00:07:47,125
[GAKUTO]
Kiyoshi... Thank you!

189
00:07:47,208 --> 00:07:48,500
[MEIKO]
No, he'll do it!

190
00:07:54,916 --> 00:07:56,083
Hey, Gakuto...

191
00:07:56,166 --> 00:07:57,333
I'm sorry, man.

192
00:07:57,416 --> 00:08:00,291
