200
00:08:15,666 --> 00:08:18,083
[GAKUTO] Sir Kiyoshi,
would you fancy some more tea?

201
00:08:18,166 --> 00:08:19,666
[KIYOSHI]
Sure, thanks.

202
00:08:21,666 --> 00:08:22,875
[GAKUTO]
I thought you should know.

203
00:08:22,958 --> 00:08:24,458
I recovered
something of interest

204
00:08:24,541 --> 00:08:26,125
lying near the refuse site.

205
00:08:26,208 --> 00:08:27,458
[KIYOSHI gasps]

206
00:08:32,916 --> 00:08:34,208
[KIYOSHI]
