234
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,375
[KIYOSHI whimpers]

235
00:09:30,875 --> 00:09:33,208
[HANA]
No unauthorized sumo displays!

236
00:09:33,291 --> 00:09:34,666
[KIYOSHI]
